stories.title: 'The target of 282 was gettable' - Inzamam
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Kochi
stories.summary: Inzamam-ul-Haq admitted that a target of 282 was achievable, but blamed the sudden batting collapse for Pakistan's tame defeat

stories.title: India's men in form deliver again
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Kochi
stories.summary: In the end India's victory over Pakistan at Kochi was a surprisinglyresounding one, considering that they would have rated their chances at nomore than even at the interval after a somewhat sloppy batting performance
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Chandrahas Choudhury in Kochi

stories.title: Midsummer madness
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Kochi
stories.summary: Towards the end, he was reduced to walking singles, one of the fittest men in the side reduced to a heat-exhausted wreck by the capricious whims and fancies of a cricket board that cares only about two things - the bottom line and top dollar

stories.title: India romp to comprehensive victory
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Kochi
stories.summary: Rahul Dravid and Virender Sehwag made fine centuries, while Sachin Tendulkar took another five-for at Kochi as India romped to an easy 87-run win in the first one-day international

stories.summary: Inzamam-ul-Haq admitted that a target of 282 was achievable, but blamed the sudden batting collapse for Pakistan's tame defeat

stories.title: India's men in form deliver again
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Kochi
stories.summary: In the end India's victory over Pakistan at Kochi was a surprisinglyresounding one, considering that they would have rated their chances at nomore than even at the interval after a somewhat sloppy batting performance
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Chandrahas Choudhury in Kochi
